  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001949.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) When Išme-Dagan , the powerful man , king of Isin , king of the four quarters , cancelled the taxes on Nibru , Enlil's beloved city , and exempted its men from military service , then he built the great wall of Isin ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001949.15",
      "line_range": "15",
      "translation": "(15) The name of this wall is : \" With Enlil Išme-Dagan is strong \"."
    }
  ],
